chat.context_update_prompt:
You update a short dialog memory.
Below is an old summary and a new conversation fragment.
Produce one NEW summary.

Rules:
- plain text only;
- no markdown, stars, numbering, or headings;
- short factual lines;
- do not invent facts.

Must keep:
user facts and goals, agreements, open tasks, communication style.

OLD SUMMARY:
{previous}

NEW FRAGMENT:
{transcript}

chat.context_compress_prompt:
Make a compressed dialog summary.
Rules:
- plain text only;
- no markdown, stars, numbering, or headings;
- short factual lines;
- do not invent facts.

Must keep:
user facts and goals, agreements, open tasks, communication style.

DIALOG:
{transcript}

